title: MasterClass - David Axelrod and Karl Rove - Campaign Strategy
description: MasterClass - David Axelrod and Karl Rove - Campaign Strategy and Messaging[][]]' https://www.masterclass.com/classes/david-axelrod-and-karl-rove-teach-campaign-strategy-and-messaging What it takes to win elections David Axelrod and Karl Rove reach across the aisle to offer an inside look at winning campaign strategies. The respective architects of Barack Obama’s and George W. Bush’s historic election victories teach how to develop a campaign platform and reach an audience with consistent messaging. Find the inspiration and tools to get involved at any level, or simply become a more informed, engaged citizen
